{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c03481887d","title":"讽刺诗——处世铭","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑4》(内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印)，中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月28日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"296765d83b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"c03481887d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"},{"id":"d7f33dcfde","name":"谭国仁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5ebb37efe","type":"title","text":"讽刺诗——处世铭","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"5d8498c77c","type":"authors","text":"四川谭国仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"039ac37c55","type":"subtitle","text":"处世铭(仿陋室铭)    　　涤尘(四川省化工公司办事员谭国仁)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"4f3311b188","type":"paragraph","text":"才不在高，吹捧则名。官不在大，有权则灵。办公室内，唯我独尊。经理虽在上，科员管几人。干部好和坏，全凭我反映。可以摆架子、拿高薪。谁要顺我意，保他能提升，如果逆我意，管教他小心。斯人云，妙哉！余之处世铭。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"6a40b72585","type":"subtitle","text":"淘官秘诀    　　涤尘","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"2f37d774ab","type":"paragraph","text":"怪哉××，性情乖张，既非经理，也非科长，自封积极分子，临驾乎众人之上，若问工作，很不那样，专靠两片嘴唇道短长，搜集群众情况，添枝添叶，加工整理报科长，功劳记上。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"634766b03a","type":"paragraph","text":"揣摩领导意图，处处举手鼓掌，是短也说长，是园也说方，领导巴掌打脸上，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"70c48ef22d","type":"subtitle","text":"八项注意","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"03ad5af4a5","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，对经理应有特殊照顾，自行车价值必须在400元以上，办公室内设备必须舒适美观。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"bca18fb484","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，凡是老干部不论其德才如何，均应提拔为科长。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"f11a20085f","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，凡属科长均应在生活上予以特殊照顾。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"5574e1b855","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，凡属党、团员均应提级加薪。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"3cb21286b4","type":"paragraph","text":"第五，积极靠拢组织又从不向领导提意见者，应在政治上、经济上给予优待。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"9f2d11f46a","type":"paragraph","text":"第六，爱发牢骚好提意见者，应严历教训或给以必要的处分。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"49c97259e3","type":"paragraph","text":"第七，受过处分的人必须对领导温柔恭顺，否则从严究办。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"3d391e406d","type":"paragraph","text":"第八，遇到经理应该鞠躬。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"330229548b","type":"paragraph","text":"以上系本人根据近来揭发的事实代三大主义领导所拟。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"b90e5743ac","type":"subtitle","text":"布告","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"c3cc3f0721","type":"paragraph","text":"查自“三大纪律、八项注意”公布以来，执行逐趋松懈，为严肃纪律，以维护法律尊严，除重申前令外，在作如下补充，务须严格执行，如有违犯者，定严惩不贷。    切切","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"5c31dab2da","type":"paragraph","text":"此令","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"efb08c470b","type":"paragraph","text":"经理××月××日","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"b46e6e3963","type":"subtitle","text":"补充规定","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"1673e938f0","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，“积极分子”加强监督，每日不得无情况汇报。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"db6ec195be","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，汇报工作应生动具体，必需有艺术性的夸张。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"c0a767f7a0","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，对领导批评者，视作落后分子论处。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"5a16e5bc10","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，如违领导意图，好发牢骚，视其情节轻重分别以大小会斗争之。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"bfa44fb98b","type":"paragraph","text":"第五，如累教不改，视其情节轻重，分别给予调出、撤职、开除等处分。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"9ec7486d1b","type":"paragraph","text":"第六，凡对“三大纪律、八项注意”不满者，一经查出将分别给予目无领导、对抗领导、立场不稳、抗拒改造、思想反动等帽子，以惩玩忽。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"7f02ddfcff","type":"paragraph","text":"第七，凡对三大纪律、八项注意以及上项补充规定执行有成绩者，视其成绩大小给予记功、表扬、补助、加薪、提职……等，以资鼓励。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"},{"id":"4e5150097c","type":"paragraph","text":"注：此系根据座谈记录，代三大主义的领导所拟。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d"}],"page":{"id":"b46d217225","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c03481887d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}